# Real Seed Values — PRIVATE (gitignored)

⛔ This file is a template. Copy it to `seed.local.md` and fill in your real
numbers. `seed.local.md` is gitignored and must never be committed.
`seed.local.md.example` is safe to commit — it contains no real amounts.

## How to use

1. `cp data/personal/seed.local.md.example data/personal/seed.local.md`
2. Replace every `X` placeholder with your real value
3. Use `seed.local.md` as reference when entering amounts in-app

These values are documentation only — the app does not read this file.
Amounts go into the app manually (or via CSV import for historical data).

---

## Wallet opening balances

Set these as `balance_cents` when creating wallets in-app.
Use the balance on the day you start using Fintom, before importing history.

- Cash                 €X,XXX.XX  (type: cash)
- Giro Comdirect      €X,XXX.XX  (type: checking)
- Trade Republic      €X,XXX.XX  (type: savings)
- Monefit             €X,XXX.XX  (type: p2p)

