## Recurring rules

Match these to the 8 rules seeded by `seed.ts`. Edit each rule in-app to
set the correct `amount_cents` (integer cents — €12.50 = 1250).

- Salary          €X,XXX.XX income, Comdirect, monthly 24th
- Rent            €X,XXX.XX expense, Comdirect, monthly 1st (Home)
- Strom           €XX.XX expense, Comdirect, monthly 1st (Utilities)
- Internet        €XX.XX expense, Comdirect, monthly (Bills & Fees)
- Investment      €XX.XX expense, Trade Republic, monthly 2nd
- Education       €XX.XX expense, Trade Republic, monthly 6th
- Radio Tax       €XX.XX expense, Comdirect, quarterly 15th
- Sport           €XX.XX expense, Comdirect, weekly Friday (ends June 30)

